cult_favorites.title: Cult Classics
cult_favorites.description: Interstellar camp, surreal humor, insane genre mashups, and other under-the-radar gems that have inspired diehard fans.

7944.title: The Cop in Blue Jeans
7944.description: In this ultra-violent thriller, a hard-nosed undercover cop (Tomas Milian) will stop at nothing to take down the criminal empire of a ruthless mob boss (Jack Palance).

229877.title: Carnival of Souls
229877.description: After a traumatic accident, a woman becomes drawn to a mysterious abandoned carnival.

231013.title: MST3K - Gunslinger
231013.description: The widow of a murdered sheriff attempts to clean up the crime in her small town with help from the man hired to kill her.

255761.title: Elvira's Movie Macabre: Maneater of Hydra
255761.description: While vacationing in the Mediterranean, a group of tourists pay to spend a weekend exploring a lush island occupied by the botanist Baron von Weser and his bloodthirsty, carnivorous plants.

257166.title: Cannibal Girls
257166.description: Eugene Levy and Andrea Martin star in this Canadian horror spoof as a couple on a romantic holiday who settle into a quaint little bed-and-breakfast run by a trio of flesh-eating ladies who fancy them for tomorrows menu.

269877.title: Fitzcarraldo
269877.description: The story of Brian Sweeney Fitzgerald, an extremely determined man who intends to build an opera house in the middle of a jungle.

272799.title: Q: The Winged Serpent
272799.description: A thief helps two detectives locate a savage cult that has summoned an ancient Aztec god to terrorize New York City in this fantasy thriller.

275215.title: Mark of the Astro Zombies
275215.description: Evil Aliens from a distant asteroid invade the Earth to create half- human robots with synthetic blood and body parts Astro-Zombies! The soulless androids terrorize and indiscriminantly slaughter Earth's humans in a non-stop killing rampage. Key members of the U.S. presidential staff are kidnapped to electronically extract knowledge that will assist the space creatures in their diabolical quest. When a squad of advanced extra-terrestrial beings arrives to assist Earth's helpless population, they begin an all-out battle to destroy the evil alien forces.

287497.title: Godzilla, King of the Monsters!
287497.description: A 400-foot dinosaur-like beast, awoken from undersea hibernation off the Japanese coast by atomic-bomb testing, attacks Tokyo.

295227.title: The Cabinet of Dr. Caligari
295227.description: Silent. Dr. Caligari's somnambulist, Cesare, and his deadly predictions.

295881.title: The Compleat Al
295881.description: The not entirely true mockumentary of Weird Al Yankovic, taking you behind the scenes, from childhood through his early-career rise to stardom.

300241.title: Cecil B. Demented
300241.description: Guerrilla moviemakers kidnap a movie goddess (Melanie Griffith) and force her to star in their underground movie.

300846.title: The Wraith
300846.description: A mysterious black turbo racing car appears and challenges a murderous gang leader to a series of races. The driver's identity may surprise everyone.

301149.title: Clifford
301149.description: When his parents go to Hawaii, a devious, difficult 10-year-old stays with his uncle and causes him endless trouble in this dark comedy.

301349.title: Parents
301349.description: In this black comedy set in 1950s suburbia a man comes to suspect that his conventional parents have a little secret which they have kept from him.

302249.title: Ski Patrol
302249.description: The fun-loving guys of the ski patrol must outsmart an obnoxious group of ski instructors hired by a developer to sabotage and create havoc in a wacky ski resort.  From the producer of the "POLICE ACADEMY" series.

302250.title: Ski School
302250.description: It's preps vs. party animals when rival ski schools compete. With their reputation and jobs at stake, the rabblerousers of Section 8 hit the slopes.

302258.title: Tank Girl
302258.description: A mega-villain controls the world's water supply, and it's up to Tank Girl and her cohorts to end his reign.

302691.title: Killer Klowns From Outer Space
302691.description: Send in the clowns, this cult classic is back! One-of-a-kind alien invasion sci-fi featuring blood drinking alien clowns harvesting a small city.

302705.title: Lifeforce
302705.description: A space shuttle discovers an alien spacecraft containing three frozen creatures. The crew decides to bring them to Earth, where they soon awaken...

302737.title: Troll 2
302737.description: While vacationing in the country, a family learns that the town they’re visiting is populated by trolls in disguise that plan on eating them.

303016.title: X: The Man with the X-Ray Eyes
303016.description: Involved in research seeking to increase the power of the human eye, a scientist decides to test a new serum on his own eyes which would allow him to see with X-ray vision.  He lives to regret it...

305029.title: UHF
305029.description: The manager of a small-time UHF station inadvertently hits it big with his strange programming ideas to keep Channel 62 from going down the tubes.

305792.title: The Adventures Of Buckaroo Banzai
305792.description: A rock-star/brain-surgeon/comic-book-hero/samurai must stop evil creatures from the 8th dimension who want to conquer our dimension.

305818.title: Harley Davidson And The Marlboro Man
305818.description: Two modern-day "Robin Hoods" heist an armored car full of drugs, putting them in the sights of hired killers and on a ride for their lives.

306942.title: Pumpkin
306942.description: A sorority girl agrees to coach disabled athletes to make her chapter look good, but unexpectedly falls for the player she is assigned to.

312171.title: Cherry 2000
312171.description: In what used to be the American Southwest, a woman mercenary is hired to bust into a 21st-century robot warehouse which is operated by psychos.

312178.title: Foxy Brown
312178.description: After her brother betrays her, a woman goes undercover as a prostitute in order to find the gangsters who killed her boyfriend — and get revenge.

312196.title: Showgirls
312196.description: An aspiring Las Vegas showgirl works as a stripper in order to claw her way up in the world, using sex and seduction to get what she wants.

314041.title: 13 Nights of Elvira: Night of the Living Dead
314041.description: Elvira resurrects the original zombie classic, and devours it with raw energy!  Elvira loves George A Romero's masterpiece so much, she's takin it to the grave!

314043.title: 13 Nights of Elvira: Shrunken Heads
314043.description: Elvira is put through the ringer, and hung out to dry, after sitting through this movie.  She should have quit while she was a head!

314044.title: 13 Nights of Elvira: Hideous
314044.description: Elvira always says, when you can't say something nice about a movie, come sit by her.    And with this movie, she got plenty to say!

314048.title: 13 Nights of Elvira: Puppet Master
314048.description: The cult classic gets the hook, when Elvira's pulling the strings.  There's more Punch than Judy in this cinematrocity.

314049.title: 13 Nights of Elvira: Demonic Toys
314049.description: No one likes playthings more than the Mistress of the Dark.  But these toys are straight out of Hell's toybox.   Playtime is over!

324874.title: Samurai Cop
324874.description: This brutal action adventure stars genre staples Robert Z'Dar, Matt Hannon, and Gerald Okamura. A cabal of Japanese mobsters known as the Katana Gang is taking over the streets of Los Angeles. With the regular police unable to stop them, it's up to maverick cop Joe “the Samurai” Marshal to use his sword and martial arts expertise to bring the crooks down.

326260.title: Suspiria
326260.description: A series of gruesome murders and inexplicable events lead a new student to suspect something evil is at play at a prestigious ballet academy.

358570.title: Bubba Ho-Tep
358570.description: An aging Elvis joins forces with a fellow nursing home resident who believes he's JFK to fight a mummy who wants to steal the souls of the elderly.

376085.title: Film House Fever
376085.description: A compilation of film clips and trailers from exploitation films, hosted by actor Steve Buscemi.

376092.title: The Gate
376092.description: Two boys discover treasure in a hole in their backyard but inadvertently open a gate to Hell, unleashing demons into their home.

376142.title: High Tension
376142.description: Best friends Marie and Alexa head to a secluded farmhouse for a quiet night to study, but a late-night visitor brings a haunting change of plans.

399606.title: Starcrash
399606.description: A pair of smugglers are recruited by the emperor to rescue his missing son while they track down a mysterious super weapon designed by an evil count.

400850.title: Meatballs
400850.description: In this classic comedy, camp counselor Tripper guides a collection of lovable campers and libidinous staff through the pleasures of a coed summer,

404566.title: The Adventures of Priscilla, Queen of the Desert
404566.description: For three drag-queen showgirls, a four-week engagement in Australia was the dream of a lifetime, but getting there intact may be a huge drag.

404623.title: Battle Royale
404623.description: A group of students from a Japanese high school are forced to compete in a battle, killing one another until only one is left standing.

413164.title: Freeway
413164.description: A teenage delinquent goes to live with her grandmother but on her way, she meets a charming serial killer and things go downhill from there.

417716.title: Buffalo 66
417716.description: Billy Brown just got out of jail. Now he’s going to serve some real time. He’s going home.

417723.title: The Lords of Salem
417723.description: When a local DJ plays a mysterious record from "The Lords," evil forces from a Salem, Massachusetts legend unleash terror upon the modern-day town.

432267.title: Night of the Comet
432267.description: When a passing comet snuffs out most of humanity, a pair of very ’80s Valley Girls hit the mall and battle hordes of blood-thirsty zombies.

437414.title: Tucker & Dale vs. Evil
437414.description: A group of college kids mistake Tucker and Dale for killer hillbillies and, when one goes missing, the misconception grows—along with the body count.

438042.title: Goon
438042.description: A bouncer looking for purpose takes his fighting skills to the hockey rink where his epic brawls could make him a star—if he can learn how to skate.

438053.title: Chocolate (Subtitled)
438053.description: When a young girl finds a list of debtors in her ailing mother's diary, she sets upon a violent quest to collect payment for medical expenses.

446072.title: Meatball Machine
446072.description: When alien parasites take control of human beings and change them into repulsive monsters, a dizzying, full-splatter, cyberpunk battle begins.

447847.title: Shivers
447847.description: The unsuspecting residents of an apartment building are in danger of being wiped out after a twisted medical experiment goes awry.

447913.title: But I'm a Cheerleader
447913.description: A naive cheerleader is sent to a gay conversion camp when her strait-laced parents and friends suspect her of being a lesbian in this quirky comedy.

448255.title: Bad Lieutenant
448255.description: A corrupt New York City cop seeks redemption while investigating the rape of a young nun and battling the addictions that drive him toward insanity.

448259.title: 2001 Maniacs
448259.description: Friends on a road trip think they've found the perfect place to party, but the locals have a sick tradition that puts them all in mortal danger.

449489.title: Skyscraper
449489.description: Far above the streets below, a gorgeous and talented chopper pilot takes on a maniac and his henchmen in a high-rise overlooking Los Angeles.

449562.title: Mazes and Monsters
449562.description: When a college student and his pals play their favorite board game in a fabled local cavern, fantasy and reality merge into a harrowing escapade.

451635.title: Zoombies
451635.description: When a rapidly spreading virus turns animals of a safari park into the undead, those left inside must stop them before they zombify the whole city.

451666.title: Iron Sky
451666.description: The Nazis set up a secret base on the dark side of the moon in 1945 where they hide out and plan to return to power in 2018.

453693.title: Four Lions
453693.description: Four idiotic terrorists push their fuzzy dreams of jihad to the breaking point, as their beliefs and methods clash, in this far-out British farce.

456063.title: Class of 1984
456063.description: A new teacher at a troubled inner-city high school ends up clashing with the delinquent leader of a punk posse that runs the school.

458078.title: Mac and Me
458078.description: A young extraterrestrial lost on Earth finds an ally in a wheelchair-bound boy, and in friendship, they find magic and a sense of where they belong.

463117.title: Puppetmaster
463117.description: A group of psychics end up in a battle with a master puppeteer who has discovered the secret of death in the form of five murderous puppets.

463838.title: The Last Unicorn
463838.description: A brave unicorn and a magician fight an evil king who is obsessed with attempting to capture the world's unicorns.

465004.title: Capricorn One
465004.description: A NASA Mars mission won't work, and its funding is endangered, so they decide to fake it just this once. But then they have to keep the secret.

465154.title: Slumber Party Massacre
465154.description: In this cult horror classic, a maniac on the loose takes his weapon of choice, a huge power drill, to a gathering of unsuspecting young women.

465155.title: Saturn 3
465155.description: Lovers who dwell on a space station amidst Saturn’s asteroid fields are invaded by an ambitious technocrat from Earth and his giant, evil robot.

465159.title: The Man in the Iron Mask
465159.description: The Musketeers’ plot to replace Louis XIV with the rightful heir to his throne backfires when the cruel king locks up his twin in the Bastille.

466020.title: American Ninja
466020.description: An amnesia-stricken soldier transforms into a one-man fighting machine, skilled in the art of ninjutsu, to bring down a ring of gun runners.

466376.title: Invaders from Mars
466376.description: No one believes a boy who says he saw a spaceship landing near his home, except the alien vampires who plan to feed on his parents and neighbors.

466377.title: Masters of the Universe
466377.description: A brave warrior must free a beautiful sorceress imprisoned by an evil ruler, but the key has been hidden on Earth and found by a teenage duo.

466618.title: Teen Witch
466618.description: On the cusp of her 16th birthday, a high-school nobody discovers she has magical powers that may help her cast a spell on her dream guy.

466902.title: Living in Oblivion
466902.description: A low-budget filmmaker struggles to keep his vision alive on the disaster-plagued, sexually overheated set of his latest indie opus.

469264.title: Warlock Moon
469264.description: When a female college student and a reporter take a trip to the country, horror soon awaits them in a closed-down resort owned by an evil, old woman.

469272.title: Starstruck
469272.description: Against the wishes of her working class family, a Sydney teenager sets out to make a splash as a rock singer, with the help of her oddball cousin.

469286.title: Firecracker
469286.description: A buxom martial-arts master dishes out justice to ferocious gangsters while investigating the mysterious disappearance of her sister.

469308.title: Rabid
469308.description: An experimental surgery leaves an injured motorcyclist with a thirst for human blood, spreading a disease that turns people into ravenous monsters.

469532.title: Night Vision
469532.description: A maverick detective and his rookie partner hunt down a publicity-obsessed serial killer, who records his victims' deaths for posterity.

472705.title: Double Dragon
472705.description: Based on the video game, two teenage brothers use their fighting prowess to take on a rich mega-villain who's after their magical medallion.

473981.title: The Plague Dogs
473981.description: When a pair of dogs escape from a government research lab, they struggle to survive under harsh circumstances in the wild, with help from a wily fox.

475898.title: Heathers
475898.description: When a snobbish high school clique threatens to ruin her reputation, a teenage girl teams up with a sociopath and plots to kill the cool kids.

475910.title: Elvira: Mistress of the Dark
475910.description: With dreams of performing on the Vegas strip, a buxom TV host tries to raise her own budget, but her outlandish methods get her into some trouble.

476644.title: The Boondock Saints
476644.description: Irish brothers try to clean up Boston’s underworld by knocking off gangsters and become local folk heroes, as an FBI agent traces their bloody trail.

478276.title: Wicked City
478276.description: The only barrier that can protect the citizens of the human world from an opposing world of demons is a secret police force known as the Black Guard.

480176.title: C.H.U.D.
480176.description: A photographer and his girlfriend become aware of a conspiracy involving a corrupt official and cannibalistic monsters, who dwell in NYC’s sewers.

480255.title: Maniac Cop II
480255.description: A formerly heroic cop returns from the dead and joins forces with a psychotic serial killer to destroy his enemies and settle scores.

484802.title: 1990: The Bronx Warriors
484802.description: When the Bronx is lost to motorcycle gangs and marauding warriors, a ruthless mercenary is enlisted to retrieve a young woman by her corrupt father.

486616.title: Trailer Park Boys
486616.description: After our favorite residents of Sunnyvale Trailer Park wind up in prison, they must hatch a plan to pull off their biggest scheme yet.

490129.title: Basket Case
490129.description: An ordinary-looking man in New York City and his formerly conjoined twin in a wicker basket are out to brutally kill the surgeons who separated them.

491603.title: The Barn
491603.description: Two pals enjoying a late Halloween night during their senior year end up taking a detour to an empty barn where evil awakens to kill their posse.

493325.title: Boiling Point
493325.description: A hapless gas station attendant on a losing baseball team joins up with a fellow teammate to seek revenge when the local yakuza kidnap their coach.

493588.title: Cannibal Ferox
493588.description: Three anthropologists out to disprove cannibalism meet men who tortured and enslaved a cannibal tribe. When the tribe seeks revenge, no one is safe.

496328.title: Dolemite
496328.description: Dolemite is the role that made Rudy Ray Moore a midnight-cult-film icon as a framed pimp who fights city corruption with his all-girl Kung-Fu killers.

497898.title: Vamp
497898.description: Two friends head for a nightclub called the After Dark Club. But when the bar’s dancers turn out to be vampires, the evening takes on a new twist.

499757.title: The Stepfather
499757.description: After murdering his entire family, a man remarries a widow with a teenage daughter in another town and prepares to do the same thing all over again.

505008.title: Bride of Re-Animator
505008.description: A doctor whose reanimation of corpses went wrong the first time tries to create a female mate with the heart of his assistant’s dead girlfriend.

508384.title: Party Monster
508384.description: Gripping true-crime story about a nightclub Influencer in New York City whose hard drug use spirals when he kills his dealer and brags about it on TV.

510564.title: Freejack
510564.description: Race car driver Alex Furlong is kidnapped by bounty hunters from the future, who have been hired to sell his body for a mind transport.

520269.title: The Lair of the White Worm
520269.description: After a mysterious skull is unearthed near a convent, village residents start disappearing, and a pagan god hungers for the taste of virginal flesh.

525260.title: Angel
525260.description: A smart student at a prestigious school, who survives by working nights as a prostitute on Hollywood Boulevard, becomes the target of a serial killer.

525409.title: Turbo Kid
525409.description: Welcome to a post-apocalyptic 1997, where an orphaned teenager must rescue his robot friend from a warlord who controls the water supply.

525825.title: Mondo Cane
525825.description: A shockumentary that explores the culture of life and death, and the taboos of sex and religion, all amidst the barbarism of civilization gone insane.

526466.title: Next of Kin
526466.description: After Linda inherits a retirement home, she witnesses a series of strange events which seem connected to a dark and unspeakable evil.

526990.title: Re-Animator
526990.description: Cult horror-shocker about a medical student and his girlfriend who conduct outrageous experiments with dead tissue after a new student arrives.

528621.title: The Craft
528621.description: The new girl at a Catholic school in L.A. meets a group of socially outcast girls who form a coven with powers that soon backfire in frightening ways.

530110.title: El Día de la bestia
530110.description: Un sacerdote católico, un ocultista italiano y un metalero tratan de cometer la mayor cantidad de pecados para prevenir que el diablo nazca de nuevo.

534184.title: Bad Boy Bubby
534184.description: The life of man-child who has been kept locked in an apartment by his mother and can only mimic others changes when he escapes to the outside world.

535827.title: Birdemic: Shock and Terror
535827.description: Midnight movie cult-favorite about a picturesque California town under attack by millions of killer birds that swoop in and wreak bloody havoc.

545771.title: I Am Divine
545771.description: The complex life of Divine, the gleefully brash muse of director John Waters, who became one of the first drag superstars of the big screen.

552251.title: Smiley Face
552251.description: A stoned wannabe actress embarks on a quest to sell a bag of "government weed" and reach a hempfest, to keep her dealer from seizing her furniture.

555703.title: Coffy
555703.description: A tough and sexy vigilante uses her brains and guns to clean up the streets and get revenge after her sister falls victim to local drug dealers.

557521.title: Labyrinth
557521.description: To rescue her baby brother, a teenage girl must take on a daunting labyrinth filled with twists and turns, controlled by the powerful Goblin King.

564363.title: The Reflecting Skin
564363.description: Set in 1950’s Idaho, an eight-year-old boy from a troubled home becomes convinced the neighborhood widow is a secret vampire murdering his friends.

569464.title: Warlock
569464.description: A 17th century witch hunter follows an evil being into the 20th century, where a young woman assists him in the capture of the wicked entity.

577930.title: Thunder Road
577930.description: A veteran returns home to the mountains to take over the family moonshining business, but soon runs into trouble from big-city gangsters and the law.

585148.title: Mallrats
585148.description: Male best friends, dumped by their girlfriends, spend the day strategizing at a local mall, in this funny, crude, and screamingly offensive offering.

594150.title: Time Warp: The Greatest Cult Films of All Time (Vol. 3): Comedy & Camp
594150.description: From Fast Times at Ridgemont High and Office Space to Monty Python and Showgirls, hear from the cast and crew who made these films cult classics.

594174.title: Time Warp: The Greatest Cult Films of All Time (Vol. 2): Horror & Sci-Fi
594174.description: From Night of the Living Dead and The Texas Chainsaw Massacre to A Clockwork Orange, hear from the cast and crew who made these films cult classics.

594929.title: Time Warp: The Greatest Cult Films of All Time (Vol. 1): Midnight Madness
594929.description: Terrific documentary made for midnight movie buffs, with clips and interviews from films ‘Foxy Brown’ and ‘The Big Lebowski’ to ‘This Is Spinal Tap.’

600660.title: Magic
600660.description: Anthony Hopkins and Ann-Margret star in this thriller about a ventriloquist whose dummy seems to have a mind of its own.

620099.title: I Spit on Your Grave
620099.description: The 1978 horror shocker about a writer at a backwoods cabin who is sexually assaulted by local savages and later returns to strike each of them down.

624951.title: House on Haunted Hill
624951.description: A suave, eccentric millionaire offers $10,000 to any of five people who can survive the night, locked up with him and his wife in a big haunted house.

630920.title: Drop Dead Fred
630920.description: Desperate for escape from her cheating husband and a life of ennui, a young woman gets an overdue visit from her impish imaginary childhood friend.

635240.title: What?
635240.description: During her vacation in Italy, a young and beautiful American tourist finds herself as a guest in a coastal villa, inhabited by a bunch of odd people.

636895.title: Batman
636895.description: After the Pearl Harbor attack, a pair of costumed secret agents are tasked with foiling a Japanese spy’s plan to mind-control American scientists.

643079.title: For a Few Dollars More
643079.description: In this classic, truly great spaghetti western, a keen, quick-witted bounty hunter and his fierce rival follow the bloody trail of a murderous outlaw.

646717.title: Return to Savage Beach
646717.description: A stolen computer disc containing the location of a mythical treasure lures both villains and L.E.T.H.A.L. agents into a dangerous treasure hunt.

646724.title: Malibu Express
646724.description: The government tasks a skirt-chasing private detective on a sleuthing mission to find the traitor selling U.S. technology secrets to the Russians.

646725.title: Hard Ticket to Hawaii
646725.description: A briefcase full of diamonds puts bazooka-toting undercover Feds in the crosshairs of henchmen working for a relentless drug kingpin.

646736.title: They Call Me Trinity
646736.description: A bounty hunter and his outlaw brother become the goofy gunslinging duo standing in the way of a craven landowner’s plan to run out Mormon settlers.

646737.title: Trinity Is Still My Name
646737.description: In the process of honoring their father’s dying wish to become famous Old West outlaws, a pair of gunslinging brothers turn into do-gooders instead.

646863.title: BMX Bandits
646863.description: Nicole Kidman stars as one third of a trio of teen BMX enthusiasts, who unintentionally get in the crossfires of a group of bank robbers.

650322.title: Breakout
650322.description: Charles Bronson and his real-life wife Jill Ireland co-star with Robert Duvall in this tale of a planned breakout of an innocent man in a Mexico jail.

650559.title: Surf Nazis Must Die
650559.description: In the post-apocalyptic future, the son of a gun-wielding woman is murdered by neo-Nazi surfers, so his mama hunts them down for bloodthirsty revenge.

652378.title: City on Fire
652378.description: A pyromaniac rogue ex-employee of an urban oil refinery starts an explosion that ricochets and causes disaster for the entire city.

654055.title: The Jerk
654055.description: Steve Martin makes his film-starring debut in the wacky comedy hit The Jerk. From rags to riches... to rags, the laughter never stops!

655405.title: The Toxic Avenger
655405.description: The free-for-all crime spree comes to an end for evil-doers after a meek mop boy falls into a vat of toxic waste and turns into a mutated superhero.

663302.title: 10 to Midnight
663302.description: When the legal system sets a homicidal maniac free, a cynical cop is left with only one option: to hunt him down on his own before he strikes again.

663308.title: Missing in Action 2: The Beginning
663308.description: A prequel to the original hit film. Colonel Braddock and his men are captured during a rescue operation and imprisoned by the vicious Colonel Yin.

663310.title: Ned Kelly
663310.description: When his mother is unfairly persecuted by police, Ned Kelly goes on a crime spree filled with armed robberies and deadly confrontations.

663321.title: Dirty Work
663321.description: Mitch and Sam need to raise $50,000 for Sam’s dad’s heart transplant. Out of work and out of options, the two open a revenge-for-hire business.

664047.title: Forbidden Zone
664047.description: Frenchy Hercules enters a door into the sixth dimension and finds herself surrounded by the kinky realm of little King Fausto and his queen, Doris.

664876.title: Crack House
664876.description: After Rick lands in jail, his wife becomes the prisoner of a drug king. Rick must find a way to save her, even if it means taking the ultimate risk.

664881.title: Rolling Thunder
664881.description: After Major Charles Rane returns home from a POW camp, his wife and son are murdered. Rane teams up with his war buddy Johnny to get revenge.

667334.title: Death Rides a Horse
667334.description: A young gunfighter forms a tenuous alliance with an aging former outlaw in order to track down and eliminate the bandits who killed his family.

667511.title: The Wanderers
667511.description: Follows the exploits of the eponymous Italian-American teenage gang in the Bronx in 1963, just before the country underwent profound change.

670407.title: The Fifth Element
670407.description: Director Luc Besson's extravagantly-styled, outrageous sci-fi tale of good against evil set in an unbelievable twenty-third century world.

670919.title: Semi-Tough
670919.description: When Barbara falls in love with Shake, their best friend Billy Clyde realizes that she's the woman he’s wanted all along!

671663.title: Losin' It
671663.description: Set in 1965, four rowdy teenage guys travel to Tijuana, Mexico for a night of partying when they find themselves joined by a heartbroken housewife.

671665.title: Poolhall Junkies
671665.description: A talented pool hustler who has stayed out of the game for years is thrust back to his old ways when his little brother gets involved with his rival.

671667.title: Rolling Kansas
671667.description: Hoping to solve their money troubles, a group of friends leave middle Texas in a beater car in search of a massive, government-owned marijuana farm.

671669.title: Sonny
671669.description: A soldier returns home to New Orleans hoping to break away from his upbringing as a sex worker, but his brothel-madam mother has other plans for him.

671674.title: The Soldier
671674.description: Terrorists take over a plutonium bomb and threaten to detonate it in a Saudi Arabian oil field. A special anti-terrorist unit is sent in to stop them.

672453.title: Fanboys
672453.description: A group of Star Wars fans hatch a scheme to steal a copy of the Phantom Menace from the secluded Skywalker Ranch for their terminally ill friend.

674393.title: Convoy
674393.description: Martin, in pursuance of a feud with a sheriff, unites scores of his fellow drivers into a convoy, rolling towards the freedom of the Mexican border.

674413.title: A Fistful of Dynamite
674413.description: A bandit and a revolutionary team up to liberate political prisoners, defend their compatriots, and risk their lives on a train filled with dynamite.

674418.title: Vampire's Kiss
674418.description: When a volatile literary agent encounters a neck-biter, he’s convinced that he’s turning into a vampire, and his behavior turns positively outrageous.

675214.title: Death Race 2000
675214.description: In a dystopian future, an automobile race requires contestants to run down pedestrians to gain points that are tallied based on each kill's brutality.

675218.title: Flesh+Blood
675218.description: In medieval Europe, Agnes, a young girl from a noble family, becomes obsessed with her captors—a band of mercenaries hungry for revenge.

675221.title: Subway
675221.description: On improvising a burglary at a shady tycoon's home, Fred takes refuge in the hip and surreal universe of the Paris Metro and meets unique individuals.

677544.title: Death Spa
677544.description: One by one, the beautiful members of her husband’s health club become victims possessed by the spirit of a scorned and insanely jealous demon.

680110.title: Road Games
680110.description: A laid-back American truck driver in Australia starts to suspect that a man driving a green van killed young women along his route.

680568.title: Super
680568.description: A super-entertaining action fantasy about a down-on-his-luck fry cook who becomes a homegrown masked avenger and puts an end to crimes.

689650.title: The Pink Panther
689650.description: The bumbling Inspector Jacques Clouseau tries to catch an infamous jewel thief before he can steal a priceless diamond from a princess.

690167.title: Meatballs Part II
690167.description: Summer hijinks involving a busload of Hare Krishnas, a space alien and a boxing match ensue when a rival camp tries to close down Camp Sasquatch.

690753.title: Shakes the Clown
690753.description: Inside the seedy underworld of hard-drinking professional party clowns, one of its booziest, Shakes, is framed for the murder of his boss.

690754.title: Screamers
690754.description: A military commander stationed on a devasted planet during an interplanetary war discovers its race of primitive killer robots have gained sentience.

693362.title: Mother's Day
693362.description: Two maniacal momma’s boys kidnap, brutalize and murder three college women in their backwoods cabin for the pleasure of their fiendish mother.

696484.title: Maniac Cop
696484.description: When a killer dressed in a police uniform begins murdering innocent people on the streets of New York City, a young cop becomes the chief suspect.

696486.title: McBain
696486.description: An ex-POW and former Vietnam War lieutenant reforms his old team in order to help a dead friend's sister overthrow a ruthless dictator.

700714.title: Too Much Sun
700714.description: When their multimillionaire father dies, two gay siblings must find a way to produce an heir in order to inherit his fortune.

702699.title: Ichi the Killer
702699.description: When a mysterious assassin abducts his boss, a yakuza enforcer goes on a tear of violent retribution with the help of a trained killer.

703601.title: Carter's Army
703601.description: During WWII, a racist Army captain assigned to an all-Black company is forced to share his command as they aim to take a bridge from the Nazis.

714188.title: Number One with a Bullet
714188.description: After a blunder sends them to desk jobs, narcotics detectives Hazeltine and Berzak decide it’s time to take the law into their own hands.

714476.title: National Lampoon's Senior Trip
714476.description: After being required to write a letter to the President suggesting ways to improve education, a group of high school slackers head off to Washington.

714951.title: Quick Change
714951.description: A trio of first-time bank robbers commits an audaciously perfect crime but miscalculates the task of getting out of New York City with the loot.

715024.title: Moving
715024.description: A mass-transit engineer faces the horrors of relocating his family from his lifelong home in New Jersey when he’s offered a dream job in Boise, Idaho.

715217.title: Vision Quest
715217.description: A gentle but driven 18-year-old underdog toils against the odds to become Washington state’s top wrestler while winning the heart of a young drifter.

715447.title: Welcome to Collinwood
715447.description: Five hapless misfits from the streets of Cleveland band together to pull off an easy crime with a huge payoff, but their plan quickly goes awry.

716001.title: The Salton Sea
716001.description: The crystal meth addicts have no idea widower Danny Parker is a police informant and the police don't know he's hellbent on exacting revenge.

716243.title: The Barbarians
716243.description: In the time of dungeons, dragons and sorcery, the fate of an enslaved queen made to wed an evil ruler will one day fall in the hands of her children.

716397.title: Club Paradise
716397.description: A burned-out fireman and a reggae singer turn a run down tropical island into a resort paradise for a group of unsuspecting, affluent tourists.

716866.title: Joe's Apartment
716866.description: A New York transplant rents a seedy apartment inhabited by thousands of singing, dancing cockroaches who help him woo a girl and avoid eviction.

724318.title: The Stuff
724318.description: Nobody knows how it's made or what's in it, but people are lining up to buy the mysterious gooey treat with a delicious flavor to die for.

724351.title: Death Becomes Her
724351.description: When a jealous actress discovers an immortality treatment, she decides to take advantage of it to become young again and outshine her rival.

724847.title: Greener Grass
724847.description: An eccentric and competitive soccer mom is slowly driven insane by her irrepressible drive to please. Suburbia has never been so absurdly spoofed.

100000089.title: Enter the Void
100000089.description: An American drug dealer living in Tokyo takes a psychedelic, acid trip-like journey into the afterlife when he’s killed in a deal gone bad.

100000214.title: Last Action Hero
100000214.description: Jack Slater, a larger-than-life movie hero, helps a young man save his world from an assassin hell-bent on taking it over for himself.

100000217.title: Saving Silverman
100000217.description: It takes a woman with the looks of an angel and the demeanor of the devil to test an inseparable friendship three men have shared since grade school.

100000440.title: Gremlins 2: The New Batch
100000440.description: The gremlins are back and they’ve taken up residence in a Manhattan skyscraper. When the rules are broken, the Big Apple will never be the same.

100000441.title: Gremlins
100000441.description: Billy’s furry Christmas present comes with three simple rules: keep him away from bright lights, don’t get him wet, and never feed him after midnight.

100001038.title: The Heavenly Kid
100001038.description: A lonely teen gets divine intervention when a hip guardian angel trying to earn his wings comes down to teach the high schooler how to be cool.

100001428.title: Joe Versus the Volcano
100001428.description: Life begins with a journey around the world for a squashed bug of a guy under the heel of a hideous corporation just as he’s told he’s about to die.

100001779.title: Martin
100001779.description: Martin, a young man who believes himself to be a vampire, moves to a small Pennsylvania town, where he begins to wreak havoc among the community.

0300005291.title: Danger 5
0300005291.description: Set in a dystopian version of the year 1982, five spies set out to kill Adolf Hitler before he kills them to achieve world domination by Christmas.

01117.title: Super Sentai Zyuranger
01117.description: Shout! Factory TV presents Super Sentai! Ky_ry_ Sentai Zyuranger is a Japanese tokusatsu television series and the sixteenth installment in the long-running Super Sentai franchise of superhero programs.

04749.title: The Aquabats! Super Show!
04749.description: A rock band consisting of five superheroes battle monsters in a retro campy style, complete with fake commercials and the heroes in cartoon form.

0300009213.title: Trailer Park Boys: The SwearNet Show
0300009213.description: Take three Trailer Park Boys, add one dysfunctional TV network, stir in a bunch of illicit activity and a healthy dose of profanity.
